###############################################
Multilingual Module
###############################################

Maintainer Contact
-----------------------------------------------
Herbert Cuba Garcia
<herbert (at) kreationsbyran (dot) se>

Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
Tested on Silverstripe 2.4.6

Documentation
-----------------------------------------------
This module allows you to add multilanguage fields to your page/dataobjects.
Read more on http://www.kreationsbyran.se/blogg/multilingual-module-for-silverstripe/

Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
1. Place this module in your root of your Silverstripe installation. 
2. Change your settings like langs and add multilanguage fields as you prefer in multilanguage/_config.php. 
3. Run yoursitename.com/dev/build/?flush=1.

Usage Overview
-----------------------------------------------
Use this module if you want to add multilanguage to your site in
an easy way.
